# 🧑‍💼 HR Admin & Employee UI Screens – Digital Talent Management System  

## 💻 Overview  
These UI screens are designed to support **role-based access and workflows** for both HR Admin and Employees. The designs ensure efficient task management, data visibility, and smooth interaction across desktop and mobile platforms.

---

## 🎯 Design Goals  
- Enable **role-based user experience**  
- Provide **efficient task and data management**  
- Ensure **consistency across desktop and mobile**  
- Maintain **clean and minimal UI design**  

---

## 👤 HR Admin Screens  

### 💻 Desktop Screens  
The HR Admin has full access to manage system-wide operations.

#### 🔹 Screens Designed  
- 📊 **Dashboard**  
  - Overview of key metrics and activities  
  - Quick insights into system performance  

- 📋 **Task Management**  
  - Create, assign, and track tasks  
  - Monitor task status and progress  

- 👥 **Directory**  
  - View and manage employee records  
  - Search and filter user data  

- ✅ **Approval**  
  - Approve or reject requests  
  - Manage workflows and decisions  

- 🛠️ **Admin Panel**  
  - Manage users, roles, and system settings  
  - Full control over platform configuration  

---

### 📱 Mobile Screens  
Optimized for quick access and on-the-go management.

#### 🔹 Screens Designed  
- 📊 **Dashboard (Mobile)**  
  - Simplified overview of metrics  
  - Easy navigation and quick insights  

- 📋 **Tasks (Mobile)**  
  - View and update task status  
  - Quick actions for efficiency  

- 👥 **Directory (Mobile)**  
  - Access employee data  
  - Search and basic management  

- ✅ **Approval (Mobile)**  
  - Approve/reject requests quickly  
  - Real-time updates  

- 🛠️ **Admin Panel (Mobile)**  
  - Limited admin controls  
  - Quick user and system actions  

---

## 👨‍💻 Employee Screens  

### 💻 Desktop (Website)  

#### 🔹 Screens Designed  
- 📊 **Dashboard**  
  - View personal performance and updates  
  - Quick overview of assigned tasks  

- 📋 **Tasks**  
  - View assigned tasks  
  - Update progress and mark completion  

---

### 📱 Mobile  

#### 🔹 Screens Designed  
- 📊 **Dashboard (Mobile)**  
  - Quick overview of tasks and updates  
  - Simplified and user-friendly interface  

---

## 🔄 Role-Based Experience  

- **HR Admin** → Full system control and management  
- **Employee** → Limited access focused on personal tasks and data  

- Ensures **clear separation of responsibilities**  

---

## 📱 Responsive Design  
- Designed for both **desktop and mobile platforms**  
- Optimized layouts for different screen sizes  
- Touch-friendly components for mobile users  

---

## 🧠 Design Approach  
- Focus on **usability and role-based workflows**  
- Minimal and clean UI design  
- Consistent design system across all screens  
- Supports scalability and future enhancements  

